A tally of 19 people have been rushed to hospital following a fire that occurred on the third floor of City Life Building on Smith Street earlier today.Authorities have closed off the roadway whilst emergency services work to stabilise all injured.Rescue Care paramedics at the scene treated multiple casualties who suffered breathing problems as a result of smoke inhalation.Cause of fire is unknown at this stage however SAPS and the Durban Fire Department are currently at the scene.